grate (buoyancy/drag), and Reactions (lifetime/condensation). The task requires:\n   - Verifying gas linear EOS, buoyancy, drag, lifetime, and condensation\n   - Creating integration tests covering all acceptance criteria\n   - Running quality checks\n   - Committing with message `feat: US-024 - Gas particles with buoyancy, drag, and lifetime`\n   - Documenting learnings in `.ralph-tui/progress.md`\n   - Signaling completion with `<promise>COMPLETE</promise>`\n\n2. Key Technical Concepts:\n   - CuPy RawModule for CUDA kernel compilation with NVRTC\n   - Blackwell (sm_120) PTX workaround for GPU compatibility\n   - SPH (Smoothed Particle Hydrodynamics) simulation pipeline: Hash → Sort → Reorder → BuildGrid → Step1 → Reactions → Step2 → Integrate\n   - Gas linear EOS: `p = k_gas * max(rho - rho0, 0)` (gamma=1)\n   - Gas buoyancy: `accel.y += beta * (T - 293) * 9.81` where beta=0.01\n   - Gas drag: `vel *= (1 - c_drag * dt)` where c_drag=2.0\n   - Gas lifetime decay in Reactions kernel\n   - STEAM→WATER condensation when T < 373K\n   - Sorted vs unsorted array lifecycle pattern\n   - packed_info bitfield: material_id (bits 0-7), behavior_class (bits 8-9), flags (bits 10+)\n   - DEAD particles have `MAKE_PACKED(0, STATIC)` = 768, NOT 0\n   - `fused_reorder` kernel gathers all SoA arrays in one pass\n   - Lifetime and health must be manually scattered back from sorted to unsorted arrays (Integrate doesn't output them)\n\n3. Files and Code Sections:\n   - `fallingsand3d/physics/kernels/step2.cu` (verified, not modified)\n     - Contains gas linear EOS at line 67-70: `if (behavior == GAS) { return k * fmaxf(rho_i - rho0, 0.0f); }`\n     - Tait EOS for FLUID/GRANULAR with gamma=7\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/physics/kernels/integrate.cu` (verified, not modified)\n     - GAS buoyancy at lines 322-325: `buoyancy = GAS_BUOYANCY_BETA * (temp - GAS_AMBIENT_TEMP) * GAS_BUOYANCY_G`\n     - GAS drag at lines 335-341: `drag_factor = 1.0f - GAS_DRAG_COEFF * dt`\n     - Constants: BETA=0.01, DRAG=2.0, VELOCITY_LIMIT=50.0\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/physics/kernels/reactions.cu` (verified, not modified)\n     - GAS lifetime decay at lines 207-223\n     - STEAM→WATER condensation at lines 137-142\n     - DEAD particles set to `MAKE_PACKED(MAT_DEAD, STATIC)` = packed_info value 768\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/materials.py` (verified, not modified)\n     - STEAM: rho0=0.6, eos_stiffness=3.0, eos_gamma=1.0, behavior_class=GAS\n     - SMOKE: rho0=0.3, eos_stiffness=2.5, eos_gamma=1.0, behavior_class=GAS\n     - FIRE: rho0=0.2, eos_stiffness=4.0, eos_gamma=1.0, behavior_class=GAS\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/step1.py` (read for API)\n     - `compute_step1()` returns 5-tuple: (density, shear_rate, dTdt, exposure_heat, exposure_corrode)\n     - `build_sim_params()` and `build_precalc_params()` for constant memory\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/step2.py` (read for API)\n     - `compute_step2()` returns (sph_force, veleval_out)\n     - `build_granular_params()` for mu(I) parameters\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/integrate.py` (read for API)\n     - `integrate()` returns 6-tuple: (position_out, velocity_out, color_out, packed_info_out, sleep_counter_out, temperature_out)\n     - Does NOT output lifetime or health\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/reactions.py` (read for API)\n     - `compute_reactions()` modifies sorted arrays in-place, returns None\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/hash_sort.py` (read for API)\n     - `calc_hash(positions)` returns `(hashes, indices)` tuple\n     - `sort_by_hash(hashes, indices)` returns `(sorted_hashes, sorted_indices)`\n     - `build_grid_params()` builds GridParams struct\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/fused_reorder.py` (read for API)\n     - `fused_reorder(num_particles, sorted_index, ...unsorted_inputs..., ...sorted_outputs...)` \n     - 23 parameters total including num_particles and sorted_index\n   \n   - `fallingsand3d/build_grid.py` (read for API)\n     - `build_data_struct()` does its own memset internally\n     - `allocate_cell_tables()` returns (cell